OL,3,CTrans lawyers take Supreme Court
OL,4,Cruling on biological sex to European
OL,5,Ccourt
OL,7,FA group of transgender lawyers are
OL,8,Ftaking the UK to the European Court of
OL,9,FHuman Rights (ECHR) over the Supreme
OL,10,FCourt ruling on biological sex. ITV
OL,11,FNews Reporter Sam Holder has the latest
OL,13,FWords by Assistant Producer Robbie Boyd
OL,15,FA group of transgender lawyers have
OL,16,Fofficially sent a case to the European
OL,17,FCourt of Human Rights (ECHR), claiming
OL,18,Fthat the Supreme Court hearing on
OL,19,Fbiological sex earlier this year
OL,20,Fbreached their right to a fair trial,
OL,21,FITV News can reveal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
