OL,7,FIn April, the UK Supreme Court ruled
OL,8,Fthat transgender women are not women
OL,9,Funder the Equality Act 2010, including
OL,10,Fthose holding gender recognition
OL,11,Fcertificates (GRCs).
OL,13,FDuring the process, the court heard
OL,14,Ffrom gender-critical groups such as
OL,15,FSex Matters and the LGB Alliance, but
OL,16,Fno one with a GRC was consulted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
