OL,7,FCampaigners argue that this omission
OL,8,Famounts to a breach of Article 6 of
OL,9,Fthe European Convention on Human
OL,10,FRights, which guarantees the right to
OL,11,Fa fair trial, and are now challenging
OL,12,Fit in the European courts.
OL,14,FFiled last week, the application
OL,15,Farrives at the European Court of Human
OL,16,FRights in Strasbourg on Monday, where
OL,17,Fjudges have six months to decide
OL,18,Fwhether it will proceed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
