OL,7,FThe group bringing the claim, the
OL,8,FTrans Legal Clinic, is spearheaded by
OL,9,Ftransgender and non-binary lawyers
OL,10,FOlivia Campbell-Cavendish and Oscar
OL,11,FDavies, as well as the UK's first
OL,12,Ftransgender judge, Dr Victoria McCloud.
OL,14,FDr McCloud, who stepped down last
OL,15,Fyear, had applied to intervene in the
OL,16,FSupreme Court case brought by For
OL,17,FWomen Scotland against the Scottish
OL,18,Fgovernment, claiming that it could
OL,19,Fsignificantly affect legal protections
OL,20,Ffor transgender women with GRCs, but
OL,21,Fher application was rejected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
