OL,7,FSpeaking with ITV News, Olivia
OL,8,FCampbell-Cavendish said: "The impact
OL,9,Fon trans people is horrendous, but
OL,10,Factually this affects all of us.
OL,12,F"We need a society where decisions
OL,13,Fabout us aren't made without us. We
OL,14,Fneed a society that is fair and
OL,15,Fequitable, and so that's why we are
OL,16,Fdoing what we are doing."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
