OL,8,Fsaid: "As far as we understand it, it
OL,9,Fis the SC's prerogative whether to
OL,10,Faccept interventions or not, it
OL,11,Fobviously carefully considered
OL,12,FMcCloud's application and made a
OL,13,Fdecision based on the value of its
OL,14,Fcontent.
