OL,7,F"The court is solely concerned with
OL,8,Fstatutory interpretation and does not
OL,9,Fhear personal testimony or take
OL,10,Fevidence, and rarely takes
OL,11,Finterventions from individuals. We
OL,12,Fwill watch with interest whether
OL,13,FMcCloud's application is accepted by
OL,14,Fthe ECtHR or even if it comes within
OL,15,Fthe deadline to proceed."
