OL,7,FThe Scottish government claims it is
OL,8,Fawaiting the updated guidelines from
OL,9,Fthe Equality and Human Rights
OL,10,FCommission, which the UK government is
OL,11,Fusing to implement the Supreme Court's
OL,12,FApril ruling. However, the lack of
OL,13,Fcurrent detailed guidance has left
OL,14,Fbusinesses and public bodies,
OL,15,Fincluding the NHS, unclear on how to
OL,16,Fcomply.
