OL,7,FMinister for Care Stephen Kinnock told
OL,8,FITV News that the Labour government is
OL,9,F"absolutely dedicated to the rule of
OL,10,Flaw", noting that the Supreme Court
OL,11,Fmust abide by international legal
OL,12,Fframeworks such as the ECHR.
OL,14,F"If there are individuals who believe
OL,15,Fthat something needs to be challenged,
OL,16,Fthen they can bring an appeal; it is
OL,17,Ftheir right to do so," he said.
