OL,7,FGender-critical campaigners argue the
OL,8,Fdecision protects single-sex spaces
OL,9,Fand the rights of women and children,
OL,10,Fwhile trans rights advocates say it
OL,11,Fexcludes transgender women from legal
OL,12,Fprotections afforded to other women,
OL,13,Fcreating uncertainty and potential
OL,14,Fdiscrimination.
OL,16,FThe ECHR will now consider whether the
OL,17,Fclaim should proceed, a process that
OL,18,Fcould take several months.
